1) choose Makefile suffixed by your platform.

Makefile.linus    Linux
Makefile.tru64    COMPAQ Tru64 UNIX
Makefile.solaris  SUN Solaris
Makefile.darwin   Apple Darwin (Mac OS X)
Makefile.vpp5k    Fujitsu UXP/V

2) activate GRAPE5 or MDGRAPE2 definition in the Makefile, if you have 
   one of them.

3) type 'make -f Makefile.suffix' and you will get executable named 'vtc'.

4) try './vtc -h' to see available options.
